<ul id="mwAyc"><li id="mwAyg"><cite class="citation news" about="#mwt235" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite news ","href":"./Template:Cite_news"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Burkeman"},"year":{"wt":"2006"},"url":{"wt":"https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2008/jan/26/healthandwellbeing.features"},"title":{"wt":"Anger Management"},"newspaper":{"wt":"The Guardian"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAyk">Burkeman (2006). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2008/jan/26/healthandwellbeing.features" id="mwAyo">"Anger Management"</a>. <i id="mwAys">The Guardian</i>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Guardian&amp;rft.atitle=Anger+Management&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.au=Burkeman&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2F2008%2Fjan%2F26%2Fhealthandwellbeing.features&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAnger" class="Z3988" about="#mwt235" id="mwAyw"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt235" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwAy0"/></li>
<li id="mwAy4"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt236" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite journal ","href":"./Template:Cite_journal"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Green"},"year":{"wt":"1975"},"title":{"wt":"The facilitation of aggression by aggression: Evidence against the catharsis hypothesis"},"url":{"wt":"http://psycnet.apa.org/index.cfm?fa=buy.optionToBuy&amp;id=1976-02349-001"},"journal":{"wt":"Journal of Personality and Social Psychology"},"accessdate":{"wt":"July 8, 2012"},"display-authors":{"wt":"etal"},"doi":{"wt":"10.1037/0022-3514.31.4.721"},"volume":{"wt":"31"},"issue":{"wt":"4"},"pages":{"wt":"721–726"},"citeseerx":{"wt":"10.1.1.366.6962"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAy8">Green;  et al. (1975). <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://psycnet.apa.org/index.cfm?fa=buy.optionToBuy&amp;id=1976-02349-001" id="mwAzA">"The facilitation of aggression by aggression: Evidence against the catharsis hypothesis"</a>. <i id="mwAzE">Journal of Personality and Social Psychology</i>. <b id="mwAzI">31</b> (4): 721–726. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./CiteSeerX" title="CiteSeerX" id="mwAzM">CiteSeerX</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwAzQ"> </span><span class="cs1-lock-free" title="Freely accessible" id="mwAzU"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/summary?doi=10.1.1.366.6962" id="mwAzY">10.1.1.366.6962</a></span>. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier" id="mwAzc">doi</a>:<a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1037%2F0022-3514.31.4.721" id="mwAzg">10.1037/0022-3514.31.4.721</a><span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwAzk">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwAzo">July 8,</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Personality+and+Social+Psychology&amp;rft.atitle=The+facilitation+of+aggression+by+